    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 3rd level, you gain proficiency with all war weapons. However, the fervor in the arts of war distracts you from enlightenment, leading you towards the use of a cruder power. Because of this, the level of spell slots provided by blood charges is halved: they advance to the 2nd level when you reach your 5th level, to the 3rd when you reach 9th level, to the 4th when you reach 13th level and 5th when you reach 17th level.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Fanatic Spell Progression</span></strong></p>\n<table style=\"width:394px;height:333px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px;background-color:#95a5a6;text-align:center\"><strong>Flagellant Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px;background-color:#95a5a6;text-align:center\"><strong>Blood Charges</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px;background-color:#95a5a6;text-align:center\"><strong>Cantrips</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px;background-color:#95a5a6;text-align:center\"><strong>Known Spells</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px;background-color:#95a5a6;text-align:center\"><strong>Spell Level</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">-</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">-</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">-</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:39.4px;height:16px\">4</td